A '''Bacta Tanker''' was a type of cargo vessel used by the government of [[Thyferra/Legends|Thyferra]].

==Characteristics==
This type of ship was 300 meters long from prow bridge to stern [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]], having an almost insectoid feel about it. The ship's central section had two parts, each of which held six cargo cylinders. At the beginning of the journey, those cylinders were filled of [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] and, once at destination, they were swapped with others similar cylinders with the help of smaller ships. The returned cylinders might be empty or they could carry native goods to be imported on [[Thyferra/Legends|Thyferra]] or traded later during the rest of the journey. For armament, these ships were armed with two dorsal [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolasers]].

